import React from 'react'
import { TextField, Typography, Grid, Button } from '@material-ui/core'
import { Card, CardMedia, CardContent, CardActions, IconButton, Paper } from '@material-ui/core';
import Navigation from '../../COMPONENTS/ModernNavigation/Navigation'
function History() {
  return (
    <>
    <Navigation />
    <Grid container>
        <Grid item sm={12} xs={12} alignContent='center'>
            <input type="date" style={{width:'300px', height:'50px', color:'blue'}} />
        </Grid>
      
    </Grid>
    </>
  )
}

export default History
